{"tid":1405754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5/8 航空業罷工情況 Update","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:05:41.000Z","uid":294200,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"34fba9929002115b17e09392656dfa34e152fe44","tid":1405754,"uid":294200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"由於航空地勤是輪班輪休，<br />\n從業員如需請假，<br />\n一般需要在 duty 前預早 Call sick。<br />\n<br />\n所以今日已經大概知道一部分罷工情況。<br />\n<br />\n頭先瞓晏覺有人報夢，<br />\n截至黃昏六點：<br />\n<br />\nC 字頭航空公司地勤：<br />\n- 明天如期值勤的同事，將額外獲得 $1000 獎賞<br />\n- 公司今晚在機場R字頭酒店預留200間房，提供予有心於明天上班但因擔心交通狀況而猶豫的同事入住 （DLLM 平時打風唔見你咁好死）<br />\n- 明天上班的同事如因應交通情況需搭的士，可保留單據實報實銷 DLLM 平時打風唔見你咁好死 x 2）<br />\n<br />\nJ 頭航空公司地勤：<br />\n- 明天如期值勤的同事，將額外獲得工資 x 1.5 倍獎賞<br />\n- 明天上班的同事如因應交通情況需搭的士，可保留單據實報實銷 （DLLM 平時打風唔見你咁好死 ）<br />\n- 目前已確認 Checkin counter 請病假同事已達 120 人，影響的客運航空公司估計至少多達十多間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n配合民航處已有 1/3 交通管制員集體請病假，預計聽日航空交通必受顯著影響。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFact 已 checked，但為保障報夢者，恕不能提供內部資料輔助說明。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b076072b775dcf596b9840c0ee030f32e025434f","tid":1405754,"uid":294200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3273e39f839395aed631c8d00786d94bbf818e","tid":1405754,"uid":294200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦，雪球嚟㗎屌！<br />\n而家已知聽日過百班航班取消喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48aa0c0204da2d2833c67d9175e381535919d18d","tid":1405754,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"下次打風知道要開咩條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc239bb871838cd5b1a3af61858e30e6991aed4f","tid":1405754,"uid":294200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48aa0c0204da2d2833c67d9175e381535919d18d","tid":1405754,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"下次打風知道要開咩條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:47:25.000Z","msg":"推啦！<br />\n姐叫你推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9527987b93d751ff0f31ed653bdd4343d774aaa","tid":1405754,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"點解H字頭公司乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cc037ac62b35771179d04a1242ddecec07336d","tid":1405754,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"傾條件？<br />\n叫佢自己搵林病喇"},{"pid":"e1e9601679292c3a9d4c92fe4aafbb7d19052409","tid":1405754,"uid":294200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9527987b93d751ff0f31ed653bdd4343d774aaa","tid":1405754,"uid":88689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"點解H字頭公司乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"無收到風呀，等其他巴絲更新！<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm